The Aura;;76;;87;;NC;;Shy taxidermist Espinosa (Ricardo Darín), who has epilepsy, dreams of committing the perfect crime. He unexpectedly gets the chance when he accidentally kills a shady character during a hunting trip. The victim had planned to rob an armored car carrying casino profits, and Espinosa takes over the scheme. But his lack of criminal experience and his illness put his life in real danger.;;Drama,Crime,Mystery & thriller;;Fabián Bielinsky;;2006;;Ricardo Darín,Dolores Fonzi,Pablo Cedrón,Jorge D'Elía,Alejandro Awada,Rafael Castejón,Walter Reyno,Guido D'Albo;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/el_aura